    <div class="mod-hd">
        

        <a class="redbutt j a_show_login rr" href="https://www.douban.com/register?reason=review" rel="nofollow">
            <span> 我来说两句 </span>
        </a>

            
  

  <h2>
    <span class="">短评</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;
      <span class="pl">&nbsp;(
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/25928157/comments/">全部 10 条</a>
        ) </span>

  </h2>


    </div>
    <div class="nav-tab">
        
    <div class="tabs-wrapper  line">
        <a class="short-comment-tabs on-tab" href="hot" data-tab="hot">热门</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <a class="short-comment-tabs " href="new" data-tab="new">最新</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <a class="j a_show_login " href="follows" data-tab="follows">好友</a>
    </div>

    </div>
    <div id="comment-list-wrapper" class="indent">
        

<div id="comments" class="comment-list hot show">
        <ul>
                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1079548301">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1079548301" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1079548301" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1079548301">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lchktk/">海阔天空在鬼混</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-08-31</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这本基于《点石斋画报》的图文互证书主要还是面向专业读者的，因普通读者很难习惯在一种完全不做解说的状态下直接读懂图画所传递的信息（乃至那些无法经由表面，而必须力透纸背的刨根究底才能传递的信息），上手之时会产生一种陌生化的感觉，需要逐渐调整阅读习惯。我倒是疑心有相当多读者可能看过第一部分的前几张图就没有耐心再翻下去了，由此我想，倘若把趣味性和时代特色最鲜明的第三、第四部分（新技术；上海都市新文明）前置，阅读效果会更理想。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="907721855">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-907721855" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-907721855" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="907721855">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/liudi678/">文的</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-04-03</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">太长见识！是一本图像与资料集，这本是新版。最有趣的部分是清末人看西洋人鬼物，脚踏车，热气球，铁路，雕像...</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1056352444">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1056352444" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1056352444" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1056352444">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/66554334/">小羊</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-06-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">做得十分用心用力，各类原始材料与点石斋的图文互相阐发，读来略为费力，不似一般图像类的书那么从容流畅。若能有选编者自己的独到阐释，就更好了</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="984924849">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-984924849" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-984924849" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="984924849">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/guming/">顾白</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-12-07</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">导读值得细读。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="958344171">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-958344171" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-958344171" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="958344171">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/80748879/">纯洁的渣叔</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2015-09-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">截取晚清的一段横截面，以图像解说历史。主题“中外纪闻”、“官场现形”：刊载之事至今亦有共通之处，感慨颇多。“格物汇编”：现今看来很普通的事物，可以想象当时给清人带来的震撼。“海上繁华”：上海无愧为当时西方文化与东方文化交流的窗口，生活方式精彩纷呈。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

